{"tid":2124370,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"連登有冇人聽Per se？","createTime":"2020-07-25T10:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T15:55:02.000Z","uid":134103,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"8dfc508ba5661728ef504a0cde10594819b30d5f","tid":2124370,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T10:37:20.000Z","msg":"Per se最近嗰首《無窮》我覺得幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v6ltnNnUfXE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dv6ltnNnUfXE&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=3d98afe0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v6ltnNnUfXE</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>除掉寂 除掉寞 還想擁有快樂<br />\n陶空心靈放縱 隨靈魂塌下已失控</em><br />\n<br />\n我自己第一次接觸Per se係佢首《逝水如斯》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eznbpqAlRy8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeznbpqAlRy8&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=d621dad4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eznbpqAlRy8</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>從這一邊到那一邊<br />\n長途萬里花連綿<br />\n盛開每個夏天</em><br />\n<br />\n好鍾意呢幾句，好有畫面<br />\n<br />\n至於我最鍾意就係《天空塌下前》，之前有一排好鍾意遊巴士河，成日搭巴士入屯門，每一次行到屯公我就會播《天空塌下前》，坐上層靠窗邊，一望到喺陽光之下波光粼粼嘅大海同理寬廣嘅天空，就會覺得心情特別好，有一種豁然開朗嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YJId-hlKy-g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYJId-hlKy-g&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=0030413a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YJId-hlKy-g</a><br />\n<br />\n<em> 就到終點 你縱然看不見 <br />\n（天空 塌下前 洶湧 退浪前）<br />\n<br />\n再難過的 任重道仍漫長 路雖漸遠<br />\n（路若漫長 靠近我 不忙亂）<br />\n<br />\n無從兌現 奮勇無悔不變<br />\n（青春 刺痛時 光陰 散落時）<br />\n<br />\n那無畏的 豔色青春 人生的 盛宴<br />\n（路就在前 請捉緊一點）<br />\n<br />\n前進的 用心開闢 未舖的路 在前<br />\n（都可改變） </em><br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a68c3d9808047577f77c0dfa054ec75abb14938","tid":2124370,"uid":134103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T10:38:57.000Z","msg":"利申：非打手，非PR狗，只係冇得出街屋喺屋企太無聊所以想分享下本地音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc68d2010f7ee7cd1934a2e42f181f297ed4f482","tid":2124370,"uid":78574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T10:39:20.000Z","msg":"聽完SITA先知都係佢地嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSITA啱聽d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b102f096b4bf01ad87fcd3923f6384dda90a5452","tid":2124370,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T10:40:09.000Z","msg":"或者有冇巴絲想分享下本土歌手嘅音樂？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6bdcb627829f2dc6d166031efdf8af53f870c7a","tid":2124370,"uid":201178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T10:41:15.000Z","msg":"推波斯雅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91c78127a7a8eb4d051bfa918c8ae38f1448a03","tid":2124370,"uid":42534,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T10:42:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7e382779d949f0fb0663a9ae2f4b7285087f2b","tid":2124370,"uid":71505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T10:44:46.000Z","msg":"近排開始聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f713a7d27b41a253bfe076e2489502e840ce28f","tid":2124370,"uid":134103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T10:45:29.000Z","msg":"一聽返《天空塌下前》又好想去海邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好掛住海浪聲同飄散住海水味嘅空氣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以大家記得做好防疫措施，冇咩特別都唔好出街，捱過咗疫情有得出返街就可以投奔初夏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(雖然到時應該過咗夏天)"},{"pid":"646e77d807d317f05909790f34e48ce051e5d88e","tid":2124370,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a91c78127a7a8eb4d051bfa918c8ae38f1448a03","tid":2124370,"uid":42534,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T10:42:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T10:46:24.000Z","msg":"佢哋亦都有唱英文歌，有興趣嘅可以聽埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7708d5ff96ab6a5087f057998a331f43126edc13","tid":2124370,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T10:48:28.000Z","msg":"ex好鍾意，btw淨係識波雅斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5188dd1ab34ce1fa486c67c0595ac704a334258e","tid":2124370,"uid":134103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T10:49:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"595232f362d39a622fa56151b703152d458a79ce","tid":2124370,"uid":83578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T10:50:58.000Z","msg":"無窮 第一次903聽個時<br />\n正WOR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 心諗咩東京喰種有中文OP?"},{"pid